subSubSection.paragraph:
The maximum likelihood tree (
Fig. 3
) based on 92 COI mtDNA sequences of 18 species including the outgroup (

Cephalopholis nigripinnis

) recovered monophyletic clusters corresponding to all species including the WIO species (

S. knysnaensis

and 

S. novemcinctus

). All these three clades were strongly supported as monophyletic groups with bootstrap>75%.
